## Business Context

**Challenge**: Allocate resources efficiently to meet demand without over-provisioning.

**Areas**:
- Workforce planning
- Equipment/machinery utilization
- Server capacity (IT)
- Manufacturing capacity
- Warehouse space

**Goal**: Match capacity to forecasted demand while minimizing costs.

